<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<body>
<p>Hi {{.Name}},</p>
<p>This is your <strong>{{.ThresholdDays}}-day warranty reminder</strong>
for <strong>{{.CommodityName}}</strong>.</p>
<p>The warranty expires on {{.ExpiryDate}}.</p>
{{- if .CommodityURL}}
<p>You can review the item here: <a href="{{.CommodityURL}}">{{.CommodityURL}}</a></p>
{{- end}}
<p>Inventario sends this so you can plan a renewal, service, or
replacement before the cover lapses.</p>
</body>
</html>
